attributionInfo.agentName: Jenny Evans, Jennifer Turnbull, Lawrence Balerio &

data.description: Beautiful Glenwood Gramercy model at The Regency in Carmella Ranch - a gated 55+ luxury community with one-of-a-kind amenities including pickleball and bocce courts, a stellar clubhouse with indoor and outdoor pools, hot tub, fitness center, and ample areas for gathering and entertaining. This home is lightly lived in and beautifully cared for! Offering unique restoration hardware throughout, modern grey color tones, grey textured tile throughout (no carpet!), white kitchen cabinets to ceiling, an espresso island, and fully landscaped private backyard with a water feature, firepit, and mountain and city views! You are close proximity to historic Virginia City, Summit Sierra Mall, movie theater, plus quick access to Mt. Rose and Lake Tahoe.
